            "text_alignment": "left",
            "margin_bottom": 34
          }
        },
        "text_block_YX3V6A": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>He is responsible for building and managing the company’s financial systems, budgeting frameworks, and performance monitoring mechanisms, ensuring that the business operates with strong financial discipline and transparency.</p>",
            "font_family": "arimo_n4",
            "font_size": 22,
            "font_size_mobile": 16,
            "font_weight": "700",
            "text_color": "#727272",
            "letter_spacing": 1,
            "word_spacing": 1,
            "text_alignment": "left",
            "margin_bottom": 34
          }
        },
        "text_block_a9JfTz": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>At Addanki’s Food Stories, Nithish leads key areas including:</p><p>· Financial planning and analysis</p><p>· Budgeting and cost management</p><p>· Financial reporting and compliance</p><p>· Investment and capital allocation</p><p>· Profitability tracking across brands and business verticals</p>",
            "font_family": "arimo_n4",
            "font_size": 22,
            "font_size_mobile": 16,
            "font_weight": "700",
            "text_color": "#727272",
            "letter_spacing": 1,
            "word_spacing": 1,
            "text_alignment": "left",
            "margin_bottom": 34
          }
        },
        "text_block_dL37kx": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>His role is critical in ensuring that the company’s growth across brands such as HAMSAA, JINAA, and FRUROOT is supported by a robust financial foundation.</p>",
            "font_family": "arimo_n4",
            "font_size": 22,
            "font_size_mobile": 16,
            "font_weight": "700",
            "text_color": "#727272",
            "letter_spacing": 1,
            "word_spacing": 1,
            "text_alignment": "left",
            "margin_bottom": 34
          }
        },
        "text_block_jJJq9E": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>By implementing structured financial controls and data-driven decision-making, Nithish Reddy helps the leadership team scale the business responsibly while maintaining operational efficiency and long-term financial sustainability.</p>",
            "font_family": "arimo_n4",
            "font_size": 22,
            "font_size_mobile": 16,
            "font_weight": "700",
            "text_color": "#727272",
            "letter_spacing": 1,
            "word_spacing": 1,
            "text_alignment": "left",
            "margin_bottom": 34
          }
        },
        "text_block_qAq7t7": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Working closely with the founders and leadership team, he contributes to the<br/>company’s goal of building a scalable FMCG ecosystem and distribution platform across India.</p>",
            "font_family": "arimo_n4",
            "font_size": 22,
            "font_size_mobile": 16,
